    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid, dependable option for someone needing a daily commuter. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including some minor door dings, light scratches on the bumpers, and slight clear coat fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some wear and staining consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it may soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up to keep it smooth. It is a functional, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
