      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in the garage, and it still has that fresh, new-car vibe. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for an adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look and see for yourself, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
