    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 996.2 Carrera 4S, a wide-body icon featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented dual-row ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a recently refreshed cooling system with LN Engineering low-temp thermostat. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a viscous-coupling AWD system, ensuring optimal power distribution. The chassis is anchored by factory M030 sport suspension, providing surgical turn-in and high-speed stability. The exterior retains its deep luster with zero rock chips or swirls, and the undercarriage is remarkably dry, showing no signs of RMS seepage. This is a turnkey, enthusiast-maintained example with a comprehensive service dossier and pristine bore-scope results.",
